➜陕西旅游烹饪职业学院协办2020“退伍不褪色、就业再启航”专场招聘会
http://www.sohu.com/a/415536808_100185418	45500
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200829/d77416984ea4457582a323f7040a7503.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200829/0b68c96a61c84fa3b16b9ce44e92b51e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200829/abaa2eb056d04cc59edc4a1c4c1e9ebe.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200829/77ac2a61014b4adcbfa701b5db586ddc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
